title: Love Reddy
overview: Love Reddy is an Upcoming Movie Starring Anjan Ramachendra, Shravani & Others. Written & Directed by Smaran Reddy. Music by Prince Henry. Produced by Sunanda B Reddy , Hemalatha Reddy, Ravindra G under Seheri studio. Madan gopal reddy , Nagaraj Beerappa under MGR Films, Prabhanjan Reddy , Naveen Reddy under Geethansh Productions.  Nizam Release by Mythri Movie Distributors.
